Russian Police Kill 17, Detain Two Over Moscow Bomb, IFX Reports

-- B y   J a s o n   C o r c o r a n
-- 
2011-03-28T16:28:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-28/russian-police-kill-17-detain-two-over-moscow-bomb-ifx-reports.html
Russian law enforcement officials
killed 17 militants in the republic of Ingushetia and detained
two members of a gang in connection with January’s suicide
bombing at Moscow’s Domodedovo Airport, Interfax reported,
citing an unidentified official from the National
Counterterrorist Committee.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jason Corcoran in Moscow at 
